ComicInfo.Title: Here Nothing Can Go Wrong (part 2)
ComicInfo.Summary: GET READY TO RUMBLE! Okay, in the place where nothing has gone wrong in fifty years it does. BIG TIME! But is it murder or an accident? Newly arrived Corporal Lane must try and fit in with these lunatics she has been assigned to work with and get to the bottom of things. But with our staff dying off one by one, how much time does she have? It's time for our would-be heroes to take things into their own fumbling, shaking hands. But armed with only conventional weapons against an alien-bred doomsday device, well, you might tickle it, or worse, piss it off! Time for Captain Andrews to come clean about what the contents of the warehouse they have been guarding all these years REALLY are. Pick up this issue for a whole bunch of surprises!
